@page "/"

<PageTitle>Index</PageTitle>

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SkinCare Pharmacy</title>
    <style>

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #0056b3; 
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .marquee {
            background-color: #5b9aa0;
            padding: 10px 0; 
            text-align: center;
        }

        .marquee h2 {
            color: #fff; 
            margin: 0;
        }

        .content {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-family: 'Rye', cursive;
            font-size: 3em;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        .leftcolumn {
            float: left;
            width: 75%;
        }

        .rightcolumn {
            float: left;
            width: 25%;
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .card {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .footer {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background: #ddd;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>SkinCare Pharmacy</h1>
</header>

<div class="marquee">
    <marquee behavior="scroll" direction="left" scrollamount="8">
        <h2>WELCOME TO OUR SKINCARE PHARMACY</h2>
    </marquee>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="leftcolumn">
        <div class="card">
            <h2>HOT SELLING PRODUCT</h2>
            <h5>Care For Your Skin</h5>
                <img src="cleanser.png" alt="Products" style="display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 65%;">
                <p>For Oily Skin</p>
                <p>Skincare products play a vital role in maintaining the health and appearance of our skin. From cleansers to moisturizers, serums, and sunscreen, these products are designed to address various skin concerns and cater to different skin types. </p>
                <GoToProducts Target="products" />
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h2>FIND WHAT FITS YOU</h2>
            <h5>Find Products Suited For You</h5>
                <img src="skincare.jpg" alt="Skincare" style="display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 65%;">
                <p></p>
            <p>There are many skin types that require different products. Find what suits you the most by making an appointment with our trusted dermatologist.</p>
                <GoToAppointment Target="appointments" />
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="rightcolumn">
        <div class="card">
            <h2>OUR MISSION</h2>
            <p>To provide accessible and effective skincare solutions to empower individuals in their journey towards healthier, radiant skin.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Popular Product</h3>
                <img src="moisturizer.png" alt="Skincare" style="display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 65%;">
                <p>For Dry Skin</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Contact Us</h3>
            <p>+65 8275 8829</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="footer">
        <h2>© 2024 - SkinCare Pharmacy</h2>
</div>

</body>
</html>
